Hi, I'm Bob Costas.
Join me and Johnny Kerr

304
00:19:45,559 --> 00:19:51,231
for exciting Chicago Bulls basketball
action here on WGN Television, channel 9.

305
00:19:51,315 --> 00:19:56,528
We weren't very good, uh,
during the time leading up to Michael.

306
00:19:56,612 --> 00:20:00,991
The team was, you know,
on a downward keel, if you will.

307
00:20:02,075 --> 00:20:04,035
[commentator] <i>They've obviously got
some problems.</i>

308
00:20:04,077 --> 00:20:05,913
<i>The ball club has not been winning.</i>

309
00:20:07,039 --> 00:20:10,876
Back then, in Chicago,
everyone was a Bears fan.

