00:24:59,873 --> 00:25:02,268
He looked at me and said,
"If you get the shot, take the shot."

393
00:25:02,292 --> 00:25:03,960
He gave me the green light.

394
00:25:04,544 --> 00:25:08,673
[commentator] <i>Thirty-two seconds to go.
A one-point lead for Georgetown.</i>

395
00:25:08,757 --> 00:25:11,384
<i>They stay in the one-three-one,
with Ewing in the middle.</i>

396
00:25:11,468 --> 00:25:13,011
<i>They've gotta look to get it in there.</i>

397
00:25:13,094 --> 00:25:15,198
[Worthy] They knew they'd be
focusing on the internal.

398
00:25:15,222 --> 00:25:17,599
That's where the defense was collapsing.

